'''拉斯穆森报导'''（{{lang-en|'''Rasmussen Reports'''}}）是一个成立于2003年的美国民意调查公司。<ref name=inside>{{cite web |url=http://www.insideview.com/directory/rasmussen-reports-llc |title=Rasmussen Reports, LLC |publisher={{tsl|en|InsideView||InsideView}} |accessdate=2012-06-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130520110558/http://www.insideview.com/directory/rasmussen-reports-llc |archivedate=2013-05-20 }}</ref>其致力于收集和发布公众民意调查信息。“拉斯穆森报导”在国家以及联邦州的层面上，暗中跟踪调查选举、政治、时事、消费者信心指数、商业话题以及总统的工作支持率。

==历史==
{{le|斯科特·拉斯穆森|Scott Rasmussen}}于2003成立了“拉斯穆森报导”，他从成立之初开始一直担任公司董事长，直到2013年7月离开创立数字媒体公司Styrk。<ref name=huffpo>{{cite news|last=Blumenthal|first=Mark|title=Pollster Scott Rasmussen Leaves Firm He Founded A Decade Ago|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/08/22/scott-rasmussen_n_3798379.html|accessdate=24 August 2013|newspaper=Huffington Post|date=2013-08-22|author2=Edwards-Levy, Ariel|archive-date=2016-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161017065802/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/08/22/scott-rasmussen_n_3798379.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=media>{{cite web|last=Siegelheim|first=Matt|title=Scott Rasmussen to Launch New Media Venture|url=http://www.rasmussenmediagroup.com/|publisher=Rasmussen Media Group|accessdate=11 August 2013|archive-date=2016-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161001181145/http://www.rasmussenmediagroup.com/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=wall>{{cite news|last=Prang|first=Allison|title=Founder Departs Polling Firm Rasmussen Reports|url=http://blogs.wsj.com/washwire/2013/08/22/founder-departs-polling-firm-rasmussen-reports/|accessdate=23 August 2013|newspaper=Wall Street Journal|date=2013-08-22|archive-date=2016-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160315095232/http://blogs.wsj.com/washwire/2013/08/22/founder-departs-polling-firm-rasmussen-reports/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=bloomberg>{{cite web|url=http://investing.businessweek.com/research/stocks/private/snapshot.asp?privcapId=52850713|title=Company Overview of Rasmussen Reports, LLC|work=[[彭博商业周刊|Bloomberg Businessweek]]|accessdate=2012-06-12|archive-date=2012-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121003231705/http://investing.businessweek.com/research/stocks/private/snapshot.asp?privcapId=52850713|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Scott Rasmsusen |url=http://www.linkedin.com/pub/scott-rasmussen/6/943/716 |publisher=LinkedIn|accessdate=11 August 2013}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Rasmussen Reports Announces a Change in Management|url=http://www.rasmussenreports.com/public_content/about_us/public_relations/press_room/press_releases/rasmussen_reports_announces_a_change_in_management|accessdate=24 August 2013|publisher=Rasmussen Reports|date=2013-08-22|archive-date=2016-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161022155313/http://www.rasmussenreports.com/public_content/about_us/public_relations/press_room/press_releases/rasmussen_reports_announces_a_change_in_management|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Byers|first=Dylan|title=Rasmussen founder leaves company|url=http://www.politico.com/blogs/media/2013/08/rasmussen-founder-out-after-disagreements-171041.html|accessdate=24 August 2013|newspaper=Politico|date=2013-08-22|archive-date=2013-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131023043218/http://www.politico.com/blogs/media/2013/08/rasmussen-founder-out-after-disagreements-171041.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

拉斯穆森在1994年成立了他的第一个民意调查公司---“拉斯穆森研究”，<ref name=business>{{cite web|url=http://www.washingtonbusinessmag.com/home/76-meet_the_man_who_takes_america_s_pulse.htm |title=Meet the Man Who Takes America's Pulse |work=Washington Business Magazine |date=Spring 2012 |accessdate=2012-07-12 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120918053019/http://www.washingtonbusinessmag.com/home/76-meet_the_man_who_takes_america_s_pulse.htm |archivedate=September 18, 2012}}</ref>这个公司于1999年被TownPagesNet公司以450万普通股收购。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.secinfo.com/dRQ1j.5p.htm |title=Securities and Exchange Commission, Form 6-K, December 1999 |accessdate=2016-09-15 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303190330/http://www.secinfo.com/dRQ1j.5p.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>于1999年开始的拉斯穆森民意调查被称为美国写照。<ref name=wired/> 2003年，拉斯穆森在[[阿斯伯里帕克|新泽西州的阿斯伯里帕克]]成立“拉斯穆森报导”。2009年8月，据[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]报道“拉斯穆森报导”收到了“巨大的发展资金投资”。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2009/08/10/AR2009081002717.html |work=[[华盛顿邮报|The Washington Post]] |first=Joseph |last=Tartakoff |title=Public Opinion Firm Rasmussen Reports Gets 'Major Growth Capital Investment' |date=August 10, 2009 |accessdate=2016-09-15 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304222910/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2009/08/10/AR2009081002717.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>新泽西州商业杂志也报道公司当年扩大了它的员工规模。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.snellingnj.com/articles-and-news/snelling-in-the-news-12142009/ |title=Sticking A Toe Into Pool Of Applicants |publisher=Snelling Staffing Services |date= |accessdate=2012-03-26 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120316105435/http://www.snellingnj.com/articles-and-news/snelling-in-the-news-12142009/ |archivedate=March 16, 2012}}</ref>

==商业模式==
拉斯穆森报导致力于收集、公开、发布民意调查信息、追踪政治圈、时事、消费者信心指数、商业话题和总统工作支持率。<ref name=inside/>{{failed verification|date=2014年8月}} 拉斯穆森报导也暗中进行国家民意调查和定期联邦州调查。公司也通过邮件简报提供评论和政治分析。2012年9月，拉斯穆森报导和电信公司成立了一个全国的电视节目，名为“美国如何看待斯科特拉斯穆森”。<ref>{{cite web|title=Telco Develops Syndie Offerings With Rasmussen|url=http://www.tvnewscheck.com/article/2011/05/24/51436/telco-develops-syndie-offerings-with-rasmussen|publisher=TVNewsCheck|accessdate=2012-02-18}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title= Pollster Scott Rasmussen to Debut Television Show |url= http://www.newsmax.com/Newsfront/rasmussen-tv-show-debut/2012/08/08/id/447966 |publisher= {{tsl|en|NewsMax||NewsMax}} |date= 2012-08-08 |accessdate= 2012-09-28 |archive-date= 2012-08-26 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20120826152317/http://www.newsmax.com/Newsfront/rasmussen-tv-show-debut/2012/08/08/id/447966 |dead-url= no }}</ref>

拉斯穆森报导利用自动化的民意调查方式包括预录电话查询来收集信息。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.rasmussenreports.com/public_content/about_us/methodology |title= Methodology |publisher= Rasmussen Reports |accessdate= 2012-06-12 |archive-date= 2012-06-22 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20120622091127/http://www.rasmussenreports.com/public_content/about_us/methodology |dead-url= no }}</ref>尽管一些传统的民意调查专家对这类方式持怀疑态度而更喜欢传统的人工协助的调查方式，但大家认为这类方式成本较低。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://voices.washingtonpost.com/thefix/parsing-the-polls/parsing-the-polls-of-auto-dial.html |title= The Pros and Cons of Auto-Dialed Surveys |publisher= [[华盛顿邮报|Washington Post]] |date= July 12, 2006 |accessdate= 2012-06-12 |archive-date= 2012-09-05 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20120905141325/http://voices.washingtonpost.com/thefix/parsing-the-polls/parsing-the-polls-of-auto-dial.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>拉斯穆森的自动化电话调查由脉冲民意研究公司执行，该公司许可了由{{le|斯科特·拉斯穆森|Scott Rasmussen}}发明的这种方法。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.pulseopinionresearch.com/About-Us |title= About Us |publisher= Pulse Opinion Research |accessdate= 2012-06-15 |deadurl= yes |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20120426053241/http://www.pulseopinionresearch.com/About-Us |archivedate= 2012-04-26 }}</ref>

拉斯穆森报导通过广告和订阅获得收益。<ref name="about">{{cite web |year=2010 |url=http://www.rasmussenreports.com/public_content/about_us |title=About Us |publisher=Rasmussen Reports |accessdate=2016-09-15 |archive-date=2012-03-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120326120852/http://www.rasmussenreports.com/public_content/about_us |dead-url=no }}</ref>

