=====2000年=====
在2000年的总统选举中，斯科特拉斯穆森发起以“美国面貌”为名的民意调查，是拉斯穆森报导的前身。<ref name=wired>{{cite web|url=http://www.wired.com/politics/law/news/2000/10/39727?currentPage=all |title=Keeping Track of Tracking Polls |publisher=[[连线|Wired]] |date=2000-10-26 |accessdate=2012-10-02 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121103195539/http://www.wired.com/politics/law/news/2000/10/39727?currentPage=all |archivedate=November 3, 2012 }}</ref>与当时大多数其他国家民意调查平均1.1%的误差幅度相比，“美国面貌”对[[2000年美国总统选举|2000年的总统选举]]的预测有4.5%的偏差。<ref name=lik>{{cite web |url=http://www.fandm.edu/politics/politically-uncorrected-column/2002-politically-uncorrected/gresham-s-law-of-junk |title=Gresham's Law of Junk — Franklin & Marshall |publisher=Fandm.edu |date=2002-01-08 |accessdate=2012-03-26 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120307164754/http://www.fandm.edu/politics/politically-uncorrected-column/2002-politically-uncorrected/gresham-s-law-of-junk |archivedate=2012-03-07 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ncpp.org/?q=node/20 |title=Presidential Poll Performance 2000 |publisher=National Council on Public Polls |date=2001-01-03 |accessdate=2012-06-07 |archive-date=2012-03-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120316123143/http://www.ncpp.org/?q=node%2F20 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

